Summary of Variables
Symbol	Description	Units
$NPSH_A$	Net Positive Suction Head Available	m
$H_{absolute}$	Absolute pressure head on fluid surface	m
$H_{static}$	Static head of fluid column	m
$H_{friction}$	Frictional head loss through piping/frustum	m
$H_{vaporization}$	Vapor pressure head of fluid	m
$\mu$	Dynamic viscosity	Pa·s
$Q$	Volumetric flow rate	m³/s
$L$	Length of frustum	m
$r_1$	Inlet radius of frustum	m
$r_2$	Outlet radius of frustum	m
$\rho$	Fluid density	kg/m³
$g$	Gravitational acceleration	m/s²
